metadata.name: Day 7 -Trip
metadata.description:
Day 7 - Trip

A boy is having an adventure with its companion horse. They are on a trip to find a treasure.

---------------------------------------------

A collection for the Inktober 2022 challenge. This year I chose acrylic paints to work on the official prompts provided by the challenge organizer.

The purpose of this collection is to give an opportunity for my collectors to get a hold of a physical art piece by Blooming Visions.

Everything is painted with acrylics on 297 x 420 mm paper. Artworks will be shipped straight to your post office, box or home!
